text:
[Verse]
Stars in the sky
Shining so bright
All through the night
Feeling alright

[Verse 2]
Moon hanging high
Lighting the way
Here as we sway
Lost in the day

[Chorus]
Stars in the sky
We never ask why
Dancing up high
We'll fly till we sigh

[Verse 3]
Dreams in our mind
Lost in the glow
Letting it flow
Endless we find

[Bridge]
Hope in our hearts
Never apart
This is the start
Love in the chart

[Chorus]
Stars in the sky
We never ask why
Dancing up high
We'll fly till we sigh
title: Stars in the Sky
